OL,3,CMan pays #5,000 to eat burgers for life
OL,5,FA customer has paid #5,000 to be able
OL,6,Fto eat burgers "for life" at a new
OL,7,Frestaurant because it "seemed like an
OL,8,Fopportunity I didn't want to miss".
OL,10,FMatt Calderwood, 40, stumped up the
OL,11,Fcash to give him "limitless food and
OL,12,Fdrink for life" for him and three
OL,13,Ffriends at the new diner, Super
OL,14,FAwesome Deluxe, in Manchester.
OL,16,FIt is part of a crowd funding campaign
OL,17,Fby burger chain Almost Famous owner
OL,18,FBeau Myers, who says he has been left
OL,19,Fstunned and humbled by the gesture.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/9
