OL,3,CMan pays #5,000 to eat burgers for life
OL,5,FThe money will help convert an old bar
OL,6,Fin Manchester's Norther Quarter into
OL,7,Fthe new late night burger joint, which
OL,8,Fhopes to open in just eight weeks.
OL,10,F"I'm totally blown away," Beau said.
OL,11,F"For someone to have that much faith
OL,12,Fand belief in what we're doing, this
OL,13,Ftotally gives me wings and energy."
OL,15,FWhen Beau got in touch with Matt, from
OL,16,FBlackpool, he discovered he had been a
OL,17,Ffan of Almost Famous's burgers since
OL,18,Fhe first started the concept 16 years
OL,19,Fago.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
