OL,3,CMan pays #5,000 to eat burgers for life
OL,5,FMatt, who works in the railway
OL,6,Findustry, said he was happy to help
OL,7,Fbecause he's such a big fan of Almost
OL,8,FFamous and said it "seemed like an
OL,9,Fopportunity I didn't want to miss".
OL,11,FHe said: "I guess the crowdfunding
OL,12,Fthing was a matter of good timing and
OL,13,Fa love I have for Almost Famous.
OL,15,F"Almost Famous was pretty much the
OL,16,Ffirst place I'd ever had an
OL,17,Fexceptionally good burger. It opened
OL,18,Fmy eyes to how American style food
OL,19,Fdone well could be so good.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
