OL,3,CMan pays #5,000 to eat burgers for life
OL,5,F"Before then I'd only ever eaten at
OL,6,Fyour standard American diner kind of
OL,7,Fplaces that never hit the mark. I'm a
OL,8,Fkeen BBQ man now, owning 6 BBQs and 3
OL,9,Fsmokers. I blame Almost Famous for
OL,10,Fthat as it directed my attention to
OL,11,FAmerican food and cooking.
OL,13,F"When I saw the crowdfunder pop up I
OL,14,Fsent a few emails, had a chat about a
OL,15,Ffew things and I was more than happy
OL,16,Fto back the venture, especially with
OL,17,Fthe incentive provided, seemed like an
OL,18,Fopportunity I didn't want to miss.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
