OL,3,CMan pays #5,000 to eat burgers for life
OL,5,F"I have every confidence that they
OL,6,Fwill pull this off, I love the idea of
OL,7,Fstripping it all back, making things
OL,8,Fsimple but well, using the best
OL,9,Fingredients and a minimal menu.
OL,11,F"As much as I love the madness of
OL,12,FAlmost Famous, simple done right works
OL,13,Fjust as well."
OL,15,FBeau founded Almost Famous as a pop-up
OL,16,Fstand in Manchester's Northern Quarter
OL,17,Fin 2008 after being inspired during an
OL,18,FAmerican road trip.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
