OL,3,CMan pays #5,000 to eat burgers for life
OL,5,FThere are now restaurants in
OL,6,FManchester, Liverpool and Leeds, but
OL,7,Fearlier in July he announced the
OL,8,Flaunch of the new late night burger
OL,9,Fjoint Super Awesome Deluxe, starting a
OL,10,Fcrowdfunding page to help fund it
OL,11,Fthrough offering rewards and vouchers.
OL,13,FBurger boss Beau had never met Matt
OL,14,Fbefore, but after finding out that
OL,15,Fhe's a long-time fan of the brand says
OL,16,Fhe feels "humbled" by the support.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/9
