OL,3,CMan pays #5,000 to eat burgers for life
OL,5,FHe said: "Apparently he's a long time
OL,6,FFamous fan and honestly this is what
OL,7,Fmakes everything we do worthwhile,
OL,8,Fthis for me was a dream and a passion
OL,9,Fproject and to have it mean this much
OL,10,Fto someone is so validating but also
OL,11,Fso humbling.
OL,13,F"It's like WOW someone loves this s***
OL,14,Fas much as I do and now I'll always
OL,15,Fwork triple hard not to let anyone
OL,16,Fdown - it's like you have to stay
OL,17,Fawesome and on top, people count on
OL,18,Fyou to keep the dream alive.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
