OL,3,CMan pays #5,000 to eat burgers for life
OL,5,F"Matt's made a massive contribution to
OL,6,Four campaign and it was mind blowing
OL,7,Ffor someone to come forward and do
OL,8,Fthis so early on, it means the world.
OL,9,FI'm going to welcome Matt in as part
OL,10,Fof the family now and share as much
OL,11,Fwith him as we possibly can."
OL,13,FThe crowdfunding has already raised
OL,14,Fclose to #20,000 of the brand's
OL,15,F#60,000 target, with people able to
OL,16,Fpledge from #10 for a first burger at
OL,17,Fthe new venue, through to things like
OL,18,Fbranded sneakers for #150 or an Almost
OL,19,FFamous bottomless brunch for 10 people
OL,20,Ffor #275.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/9
