OL,3,CMan pays #5,000 to eat burgers for life
OL,5,FBeau and his team are also holding a
OL,6,Fspecial yard sale in the Northern
OL,7,FQuarter on Saturday, 20 July, to raise
OL,8,Ffurther funds for the new development.
OL,10,FPeople will be able to buy a host of
OL,11,Fprops, art, memorabilia and
OL,12,Ffurnishings formerly used at Almost
OL,13,FFamous venues.
OL,15,FThey will also be serving up bacon
OL,16,Fsandwiches and lemonade from 11am to
OL,17,F6pm outside Almost Famous in the
OL,18,FNorthern Quarter.
